<br>
It shouldn't be too hard to add already existing races as PC vs NPC.  The models would have to be set to allow them in every zone and there is probably many other considerations, but at least the artwork exists for the male characters.<br>
<br>
Goblins should be easier than some others using Runnyeye as the starting city.  Gnolls could use Infected Paw as a home base.  Orcs of course could be from Crushbone.<br>
<br>
